{
  "guid": "quan",
  "name": "Quantizer",
  "description": "This algorithm is a multi-channel CV quantizer, loosely based on the Quad Quantizer algorithm on the disting EX. It supports microtuning (see above), but this is not a requirement. It quantizes CV inputs and generates CV outputs and/or MIDI output. The quantization parameters are common to all channels; the individual channels' parameters are solely related to routing.",
